[src:catch2-cpp-lib/test-automation] When automated testing is in place, regression testing can be a relatively quick and easy operation.
[src:catch2-cpp-lib/test-automation] Instead of a significant outlay of human time and effort, a regression test run could require nothing more than a push of a button and even starting the run can be automated.
